Module it.polimi.ingsw
Package it.polimi.ingsw.model.handler

Class Rule

java.lang.Object
it.polimi.ingsw.model.handler.Rule
class Rule
extends java.lang.Object
Represents a rule of the game. This class is at the heart of the representation of all standard rules and God Effects in the game. It achieves its aim thanks to a high level of detail, provided by several attributes that can be accessed through the getters/setters of the class. A fundamental principle of the class is its immutability. Attributes can be set only once and then the rule can be used by multiple users without interfering with one another leading to undesired changes in behaviors.
